  $( One plus one equals two.  Using proof-shortening techniques pioneered by
     Mr. Mel O'Cat, along with the latest supercomputer technology, Prof. Loof
     Lirpa and colleagues were able to shorten Whitehead and Russell's 360-page
     proof that 1+1=2 in _Principia Mathematica_ to this remarkable proof only
     two steps long, thus establishing a new world's record for this famous
     theorem.  (Contributed by Prof. Loof Lirpa, 1-Apr-2008.) $)
